  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier5_KillBossTwinsInfested_offer",
    "english": "The same warriors have spotted another set of twins wandering just by [DECEA3]{poi.name}[-]. It's the same, one is blue, and the other is red. But at this point, you already know that it's blue and green. But there is something new; he also described a mechanism on the back of each. Be cautious. We don't know what those things can do. Kill them before they become a bigger problem."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier5_KillBossDemolition_offer",
    "english": "The rumors are real. [DECEA3]A monstrosity has been found[-]. Explosions sound everywhere, destruction, death. The bounties are at the highest prices, even though the other warriors are too afraid to take the risk. So what do you think, are you crazy enough to accept this mission? He is just by [DECEA3]{poi.name}[-]"
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier5_KillBossDemolitionInfested_offer",
    "english": "Do you remember the monstrosity that appeared before? Of course you do. Well, now he is back and more powerful than ever. Our hunters named him [DECEA3]TYRANT[-]. I've decided to send only you with your squad (if someone is crazy enough to handle you). I've already had a lot of deaths, and I don't want to take more risks. You are part of the Elite, so I have trust that you will do your job. Last time he was seen just by [DECEA3]{poi.name}[-]."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_BuriedChestDogBossT2",
    "english": "Buried Chest"
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_BuriedChestDogBossT6",
    "english": "Buried Chest"
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossMultiplyInfested_offer",
    "english": "Something unbelievable happened, one of our food storage units was attacked [DECEA3]{poi.name}[-]. We’re not exactly sure how it all went down or how the bandits found it; it was pretty discreet. Apparently, another zombie modified by them was involved in the attack. I need you to deal with it so this doesn’t turn into a bigger problem."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossCartInfested_subtitle",
    "english": "The Cart Zombie"
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossCartInfested_description",
    "english": "I wasn’t going to tell you this yet, but the guys here kept insisting. It seems like it’s become a trend to classify the zombies, and they’re calling this one the spider\" type. I’m not sure how that could help you"
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossCartInfested_offer",
    "english": "Those bastards are both lucky and insane. The bandits managed to find a giant zombie mutated by radiation, and on top of that, they mounted a massive cannon on it. I can’t imagine who would agree to work on its back to set all that up. It’s at [DECEA3]{poi.name}[-] now. I can’t afford to lose more people in this fight, I need you to take it down."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossCartInfested_completion",
    "english": "Great job! You took it down and kept the body in good condition! Maybe we can still make some gains from this fight. Excellent work! Here is your reward."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossCartInfested_response",
    "english": "Hunt the Giant Cart Zombie ([DECEA3]{poi.distance} {poi.direction}[-])"
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossDroneInfested_description",
    "english": "This is the final boss. The ultimate trial. Be prepared !\\n\\nThis drone was made by the bandits so they can control the others creatures by distance. We can weaken them destroying this drone."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossDroneInfested_offer",
    "english": "This is the final boss. The ultimate trial. Be prepared !\\n\\nThis drone was made by the bandits so they can control the others creatures by distance. We can weaken them destroying this drone. Go to [DECEA3]{poi.name}[-] to start the fight, this was the last location that it was seen."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossDroneInfested_completion",
    "english": "That was a very though fight. Their forces should be weaker now. There are still a lot of zombies out there to be beaten. Stay prepared. Here is your reward."
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_KillBossDroneInfested_response",
    "english": "Hunt the Central Machine ([DECEA3]{poi.distance} {poi.direction}[-])"
  },
