  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier6_MobileDefenseReward_name",
    "english": "Tier 6 Mobile Defense (Reward)"
  },
  {
    "key": "ZombieINC_challenge_tier3_MobileDefense_offer",
    "english": "The mission is simple: we left an antenna device just [DECEA3]outside the trader's area[-]. [DECEA3]Approach it[-] and equip the device. Once it's on, head to the designated point [DECEA3]{treasure.distance} {treasure.direction}[-]. Because of the noise and frequency of the antenna, some zombies, especially ferals, might come your way. [DECEA3]Don't let them hit you too much[-], or the antenna might break. While you're out there, we'll be intercepting enemy faction messages, trying to figure out their next move… and who knows, maybe they'll even reveal the location of something buried. [DECEA3]PAY ATTENTION: [-]Don't forget to bring a [DECEA3]shovel[-], there might be something worth digging up at the communication point, bring it back."
  },
